Package Shared

Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shared.Course
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Course
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Provides data fields and methods to create a Java data-type, representing a Course in a Learning Platform Java application. The overall purpose of this class is to store information to display and send between the client and server of the final project of ENSF 409.

    March 5, 2018
